AuthDocsMetaDescription: ONLYOFFICE Personal is a free online editing suite for text documents, spreadsheets and presentations with an individual cloud storage.
AuthDocsMetaKeywords: edit word online, word editor online, word online free, word office online
AuthDocsPowerfulCollaborationSub: Invite anyone via links to edit documents together or get reviews on your work. Choose between multiple access rights, comment, track changes, chat, and browse version history.
AuthDocsPowerfulSheetsSub: Organize, examine, and calculate any complex data. Apply over 430 formulas. Create and edit pivot tables.  Add table style templates, change sheet views, adjust layouts and prepare tables for printing.
AuthDocsPowerfulSlidesSub: Choose from multiple layouts and style options, create schemes and infographics for any purpose, present comfortably with Presenter View.
AuthDocsPowerfulTextSub: Write and edit professionally with all formatting features you’ll ever need. Add shapes, charts, tables and other objects. Apply layout elements, add endnotes and footnotes, cross-references, page numbers and more. Review and compare texts.
